<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Kampaniyalar — Kontakt Home</title>
    <style>
        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
        body { background:#0f0f0f; color:white; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; }
        nav { background:#1a1a1a; padding:0 40px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; height:65px; position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100; border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a2a; }
        .logo { font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; color:white; }
        .logo span { color:#e30613; }
        .nav-links { display:flex; gap:28px; list-style:none; }
        .nav-links a { color:#ccc; text-decoration:none; font-size:15px; transition:color 0.2s; }
        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color:white; }
        .cart-btn { background:#e30613; color:white; padding:9px 20px; border-radius:8px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; }
        .cart-count { background:white; color:#e30613; border-radius:50%; width:20px; height:20px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:12px; font-weight:bold; }

        .hero { background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0000, #111); padding:60px 40px; text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a2a; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
        .hero::before { content:'🔥'; position:absolute; font-size:200px; opacity:0.04; top:-20px; right:5%; }
        .hero h1 { font-size:40px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:10px; }
        .hero h1 span { color:#e30613; }
        .hero p { color:#888; font-size:16px; }
        .hero-badge { display:inline-block; background:#e30613; color:white; padding:6px 16px; border-radius:20px; font-size:13px; font-weight:bold; margin-bottom:16px; }

        .container { max-width:1200px; margin:40px auto; padding:0 24px; }

        .section-title { font-size:22px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:20px; padding-left:12px; border-left:4px solid #e30613; }

        .kampaniya-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:20px; margin-bottom:50px; }

        .kamp-card { background:#1a1a1a; border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid #222; transition:transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; cursor:pointer; }
        .kamp-card:hover { transform:translateY(-4px); border-color:#e30613; }
        .kamp-banner { height:160px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:60px; position:relative; }
        .kamp-banner.red { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e30613,#8b0000); }
        .kamp-banner.blue { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0078d4,#004080); }
        .kamp-banner.green { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#28a745,#145222); }
        .kamp-banner.purple { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6f42c1,#3a1d6e); }
        .kamp-banner.orange { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fd7e14,#8b3a00); }
        .kamp-banner.teal { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#20c997,#0a5240); }
        .kamp-discount { position:absolute; top:12px; right:12px; background:white; color:#e30613; font-size:18px; font-weight:900; padding:6px 12px; border-radius:8px; }
        .kamp-body { padding:16px; }
        .kamp-body h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; }
        .kamp-body p { color:#888; font-size:13px; margin-bottom:12px; line-height:1.5; }
        .kamp-body .son-gun { color:#e30613; font-size:12px; font-weight:bold; }
        .kamp-btn { display:block; text-align:center; background:#e30613; color:white; padding:10px; border-radius:8px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; margin-top:12px; transition:background 0.2s; }
        .kamp-btn:hover { background:#c0000f; }

        .banner-full { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a1a,#2a2a2a); border:1px solid #333; border-radius:16px; padding:40px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:50px; }
        .banner-full h2 { font-size:28px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:8px; }
        .banner-full h2 span { color:#e30613; }
        .banner-full p { color:#888; font-size:15px; max-width:500px; }
        .banner-full a { display:inline-block; background:#e30613; color:white; padding:12px 28px; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; font-size:15px; white-space:nowrap; }
        .banner-full a:hover { background:#c0000f; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
    <a href="/" class="logo">Kontakt<span>Home</span></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Ana Səhifə</a></li>
        <li><a href="/mehsullar">Məhsullar</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brendler">Brendlər</a></li>
        <li><a href="/kampaniyalar" class="active">Kampaniyalar</a></li>
        <li><a href="/magazalar">Mağazalar</a></li>
        <li><a href="/kreditler">Kredit</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/sebet" class="cart-btn">🛒 Səbət <span class="cart-count" id="cartCount">0</span></a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">🔥 Aktiv Kampaniyalar</div>
    <h1>Xüsusi <span>Təkliflər</span></h1>
    <p>Məhdud müddətli kampaniyalar — fürsəti qaçırma!</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

    <div class="banner-full">
        <div>
            <h2>Yay <span>Endirimi</span> Başladı!</h2>
            <p>Seçilmiş smartfon, noutbuk və televizorlarda 50%-ə qədər endirim. Kampaniya 31 iyula qədər davam edir.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/mehsullar">İndi Al →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">Aktiv Kampaniyalar</div>
    <div class="kampaniya-grid">
        <div class="kamp-card">
            <div class="kamp-banner red">📱<span class="kamp-discount">-30%</span></div>
            <div class="kamp-body">
                <h3>iPhone Həftəsi</h3>
                <p>Bütün iPhone modellərinə xüsusi endirim. Apple texnikasında qənaət et.</p>
                <div class="son-gun">⏰ Son gün: 31 May 2026</div>
                <a href="/mehsullar" class="kamp-btn">Məhsullara bax →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kamp-card">
            <div class="kamp-banner blue">💻<span class="kamp-discount">-25%</span></div>
            <div class="kamp-body">
                <h3>Noutbuk Festivalı</h3>
                <p>Samsung, Asus, Lenovo noutbukları kampaniya qiymətilə əldə et.</p>
                <div class="son-gun">⏰ Son gün: 5 İyun 2026</div>
                <a href="/mehsullar" class="kamp-btn">Məhsullara bax →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kamp-card">
            <div class="kamp-banner green">📺<span class="kamp-discount">-40%</span></div>
            <div class="kamp-body">
                <h3>Smart TV Endirimi</h3>
                <p>LG, Samsung 4K televizorlar böyük endirimlə — evini yenilə!</p>
                <div class="son-gun">⏰ Son gün: 15 İyun 2026</div>
                <a href="/mehsullar" class="kamp-btn">Məhsullara bax →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kamp-card">
            <div class="kamp-banner purple">⌚<span class="kamp-discount">-20%</span></div>
            <div class="kamp-body">
                <h3>Smart Saat Aksiyası</h3>
                <p>Apple Watch, Samsung Galaxy Watch modelləri endirimlə.</p>
                <div class="son-gun">⏰ Son gün: 20 İyun 2026</div>
                <a href="/mehsullar" class="kamp-btn">Məhsullara bax →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kamp-card">
            <div class="kamp-banner orange">🎧<span class="kamp-discount">-50%</span></div>
            <div class="kamp-body">
                <h3>Aksesuar Bazarı</h3>
                <p>Qulaqlıq, şarj cihazı, çanta — 50%-ə qədər endirim!</p>
                <div class="son-gun">⏰ Son gün: 25 May 2026</div>
                <a href="/mehsullar" class="kamp-btn">Məhsullara bax →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kamp-card">
            <div class="kamp-banner teal">🏠<span class="kamp-discount">-35%</span></div>
            <div class="kamp-body">
                <h3>Ev Texnikası</h3>
                <p>Soyuducu, paltaryuyan, kondisioner — böyük yay endirimi!</p>
                <div class="son-gun">⏰ Son gün: 30 İyun 2026</div>
                <a href="/mehsullar" class="kamp-btn">Məhsullara bax →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
function cartSayiYenile() {
    const sebet = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('sebet')) || [];
    const umumi = sebet.reduce((c, m) => c + m.say, 0);
    document.getElementById('cartCount').textContent = umumi;
}
cartSayiYenile();
</script>
</body>
</html>
